Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 09:42:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] docs: fix inconsistencies in documentation folder

- using-azure-identity.md: Update DefaultAzureCredential chain to
  reflect the full set of credentials it tries (was missing
  WorkloadIdentityCredential, VisualStudioCodeCredential, AzureCliCredential,
  AzurePowerShellCredential, AzureDeveloperCliCredential, and BrokerCredential)

- writing-performance-tests.md: Fix tsconfig extends path from
  tsconfig.package (does not exist) to tsconfig.lib.json

- resolve-pnpm-lock-merge-conflict.md: Fix missing '/' separator before
  pnpm-lock.yaml in the git add command in the combined shell one-liner

- steps-after-generations.md: Add missing '...' suffix to pnpm build
  --filter commands so that dependencies are also built (3 occurrences
  in the Windows and Linux playback/record examples)

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
